805
00:54:36.941 --> 00:54:38.818
No, it's just a guy who wants money.

806
00:54:40.820 --> 00:54:42.363
I don't buy that.

807
00:54:42.488 --> 00:54:44.438
It's not a very good way to make money.

808
00:54:45.700 --> 00:54:49.162
So, um, what is this guy's deal?

809
00:54:50.705 --> 00:54:53.207
A while back, he held
some people for ransom.

810
00:54:53.541 --> 00:54:56.294
