813
00:55:01.132 --> 00:55:02.842
If he gets the money, he wins.

814
00:55:02.925 --> 00:55:04.385
If the bus blows up, he wins.

815
00:55:04.594 --> 00:55:05.970
What if you win?

816
00:55:06.053 --> 00:55:07.721
Then tomorrow, we'll play another one.

817
00:55:07.805 --> 00:55:09.765
