- No one gets off!

859
00:57:07.925 --> 00:57:09.218
It'll grease the wheels
with the money men

860
00:57:09.302 --> 00:57:11.053
if you show a little charity.

861
00:57:11.137 --> 00:57:13.287
There's still gonna
be plenty of us to kill.

862
00:57:14.056 --> 00:57:17.310
Okay, son, you can try
and unload the driver.

863
00:57:17.393 --> 00:57:20.980
