868
00:57:29.530 --> 00:57:32.241
Norwood, get us closer!

869
00:57:32.325 --> 00:57:34.827
- We're gonna get the bus driver...
- We're gonna get the driver off.

870
00:57:34.910 --> 00:57:37.038
- Just him?
- For now. Gigantor!

871
00:57:37.121 --> 00:57:40.082
- Ortiz.
- Ortiz. I'm gonna need your help.

872
00:57:40.166 --> 00:57:42.418
- Okay.
- Okay, I need you to pass him to me.

873
00:57:42.501 --> 00:57:44.837
WOMAN: You have to keep him
straight, or I think the wound will tear.

874
00:57:44.920 --> 00:57:46.839
- What about the rest of us?
- Hey, hey! Lady!

875
00:57:46.922 --> 00:57:48.633
What about the rest of us?

876
00:57:48.716 --> 00:57:50.176
Come on, Sam. I got you.

877
00:57:50.259 --> 00:57:53.137
I can't stay! I can't...

878
00:57:53.220 --> 00:57:56.182
- How you feelin'?
