879
00:57:56.265 --> 00:57:58.434
- ANNIE: Take care, Sam.
- Okay, Annie.

880
00:57:59.477 --> 00:58:01.854
- JACK: Drive straight!
- MAC: Keep it straight!

881
00:58:04.940 --> 00:58:06.776
Okay, Annie, get as close as you can.

882
00:58:06.859 --> 00:58:08.319
- Okay?
- All right.

883
00:58:09.403 --> 00:58:10.696
Closer!

884
00:58:11.447 --> 00:58:13.074
A little closer, Annie!

885
00:58:14.784 --> 00:58:16.827
- Annie, a little closer!
- ANNIE: Okay.

