00:58:16.952 --> 00:58:20.122
- (GRUNTING)
- ANNIE: Okay, how's this?

887
00:58:23.209 --> 00:58:24.042
Sorry! Sorry.

888
00:58:25.503 --> 00:58:28.089
Okay, Annie, no problem.
Let's try it one more time.

889
00:58:29.799 --> 00:58:31.342
A little more!

890
00:58:31.801 --> 00:58:33.636
Okay! Okay! Right there! Steady!

891
00:58:33.719 --> 00:58:35.012
Hold it steady!

892
00:58:35.846 --> 00:58:38.808
- You got him? You got him?
- (GRUNTING)

893
00:58:39.850 --> 00:58:41.769
Hold him! I got him! We're clear!

894
00:58:43.479 --> 00:58:46.816
- All right! Oh.
- I'm all right. Thanks.

895
00:58:47.024 --> 00:58:48.943
- (PASSENGERS CHEERING)
- Oh, my God.

896
00:58:49.944 --> 00:58:52.363
Yes! Oh!

897
00:58:55.866 --> 00:58:58.244
(SHOUTING INDISTINCTLY)

898
00:58:58.411 --> 00:59:00.204
