899
00:59:00.287 --> 00:59:01.831
JACK: It's gonna be okay.

900
00:59:03.332 --> 00:59:04.333
Whew!

901
00:59:05.167 --> 00:59:07.517
MAN: Come on! Come
on, lady, give me your hand!

902
00:59:07.670 --> 00:59:11.632
- I have to, Annie.
- No, Helen! No, Helen, no!

903
00:59:11.757 --> 00:59:13.884
- Come on! Right there!
- Helen, no! No!

904
00:59:14.051 --> 00:59:15.928
MAN (ON TV): <i>Here at the 105 Freeway,</i>

905
00:59:16.011 --> 00:59:18.139
