- (BEEPING)

907
00:59:22.101 --> 00:59:23.561
No, Helen!

908
00:59:24.520 --> 00:59:25.688
(SCREAMING)

909
00:59:38.909 --> 00:59:42.329
Goddamn it, Mac! We gotta get
those fuckin' choppers out of here!

910
00:59:42.455 --> 00:59:44.123
<i>...was driving the bus.</i>

911
00:59:44.206 --> 00:59:45.708
<i>Well, I couldn't tell how old...</i>

912
00:59:45.791 --> 00:59:46.792
<i>An explosion.</i>

913
00:59:47.001 --> 00:59:48.627
<i>Some kind of an explosion.</i>

914
00:59:48.711 --> 00:59:51.839
<i>The bus hasn't exploded,
but... Oh, my God.</i>

915
00:59:51.922 --> 00:59:53.883
<i>A woman caught in the blast fell.</i>

916
00:59:53.966 --> 00:59:56.343
