01:00:26.081 --> 01:00:28.083
I can't, you know.

921
01:00:28.250 --> 01:00:30.252
This is the wrong bus.

922
01:00:31.462 --> 01:00:32.797
I mean, for me to...

923
01:00:34.965 --> 01:00:36.383
I can't die here.

924
01:00:37.301 --> 01:00:38.803
Hey, shut up, man.

925
01:00:40.554 --> 01:00:42.848
- I got a wife.
- Oh, you do?

926
01:00:42.973 --> 01:00:47.645
Hey! So, if you have a wife and I
don't, does that mean I'm expendable?

927
01:00:47.728 --> 01:00:49.578
Hey, what are you talkin' about, man?

928
01:00:49.939 --> 01:00:53.067
The guy's just talkin'
crazy. It gets on my nerves.

929
01:00:54.193 --> 01:00:55.903
- Gets on everybody's nerves.
- Oh, yeah?

930
01:00:55.986 --> 01:00:58.405
Well, I think I have the
right to be a little bit upset

931
01:00:58.489 --> 01:01:00.199
after all that we've...

