936
01:01:09.375 --> 01:01:10.376
Hey!

937
01:01:25.099 --> 01:01:26.851
How are you doing? You all right?

938
01:01:26.934 --> 01:01:27.935
Mm-mm.

939
01:01:28.477 --> 01:01:29.812
What can I do?

940
01:01:32.314 --> 01:01:33.899
When that bomb went off...

941
01:01:34.859 --> 01:01:35.901
I know.

942
01:01:36.694 --> 01:01:38.028
I thought that was it.

943
01:01:38.112 --> 01:01:40.698
I thought that was the
bomb and I was dead.

944
01:01:41.907 --> 01:01:45.007
And then when I saw her body
fall under the bus, it was like...

945
01:01:46.161 --> 01:01:47.413
You were glad you were still alive.

946
01:01:47.496 --> 01:01:48.497
Mm-hmm.

947
01:01:50.666 --> 01:01:51.876
I'm so sorry.

948
01:01:51.959 --> 01:01:52.960
Don't be.

949
01:01:53.586 --> 01:01:55.504
You should be glad. We all are.

950
01:01:58.215 --> 01:02:01.302
- It doesn't mean you don't care.
- I know, but she was so scared.

951
01:02:01.385 --> 01:02:04.471
