lady who didn't deserve to get killed.

952
01:02:04.555 --> 01:02:07.641
But, Annie, if she'd gotten
off, it would've killed us all.

953
01:02:07.975 --> 01:02:09.810
He's the asshole, Annie,

954
01:02:09.894 --> 01:02:12.094
the guy who put us here.
Remember that, okay?

955
01:02:12.271 --> 01:02:13.647
Big asshole.

956
01:02:15.941 --> 01:02:17.026
Okay.

957
01:02:20.112 --> 01:02:21.530
Are you sure?

958
01:02:22.448 --> 01:02:23.949
Well, how far?

959
