about three miles ahead.

964
01:02:39.381 --> 01:02:40.966
There's a section missing.

965
01:02:41.884 --> 01:02:43.302
Section missing?

966
01:02:48.849 --> 01:02:51.810
But it's on the map. It's
finished on the goddamn map!

967
01:02:52.978 --> 01:02:55.189
